body:
This does seem to be a documentation issue.

It seems that back in June 2016,   the initial introduction of the op added in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/ea9ec0a3f938dc4db86a6d8616b7a9e62d73d49f aimed to support various types, but 7 days later this was changed to support only floats in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/1d92cfcbf5c157b3e4069741ae5bdbbea6666dc5

@gpapan : Does the op documentation need to be updated or do we need to register kernels for more real number types?
